        <updateDate>2011-07-13T21:26:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Honoring Hometown Heroes Act - Permits the flag of the United States to be flown at half-staff in the event of the death of a first responder (firefighter, police officer, or emergency medical service provider) serving in the line of duty.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
